        "description": "GLPI is a Free Asset and IT Management Software package, that provides ITIL Service Desk features, licenses tracking and software auditing. Kanban is a GLPI view to display Projects, Tickets, Changes or Problems on a task board. In versions prior to 10.0.1 a user can exploit a cross site scripting vulnerability in Kanban by injecting HTML code in its user name. Users are advised to upgrade. There are no known workarounds for this issue.",
